node.text:
And Nolan wonders why our podcast takes so long to record...😅

What's your favorite Hot Wheel or toy car?

We usually edit a lot of this stuff out but had to give you guys this one lol. Go check out our podcast Past Gas if you haven't already. This week's episode is on Wendell Scott -- the first black driver in NASCAR. He got his only win stolen from him! It's a story that we didn't really know a lot about but it's really crazy. We did a lot of research so you should go listen to it!

Search "Past Gas" on Apple Podcasts/Spotify/Google/etc. ORR if you want to WATCH us do it like in this^ clip, go to our Donut Podcasts channel on YT. 🙏Thanks yall, luv ya!

node.text: It’s been incredibly hard for @jamespumphrey & @nolanjsykes to stay quiet on the announcement that they are in DIRT 5. Today they were so stoked to hear themselves in DIRT 5 that they wanted to share their first listen with all the Donut fans! Check out their first listen and keep up with new audio drops at the link in our bio! Pre-orders go live soon and we will have more announcements soon! This is literally one of the coolest things that’s ever happened to us, thank all of you for watching our stuff and making dreams like this possible. We Love You. We’re in a video game, Dudes!
